events.text:
The Blackhole approaches, an oblivion that swallows life, time, histories, and memory.
Fear not commodore, for you might have failed to save yourself and the human race but you will soon be a shooting star.
On your way to death, you perhaps ponder…
if it’s possible for your soul to be amongst a starry night, glistening within endless darkness and be the new Milky Way?
